1
00:00:01,100 --> 00:00:03,964
The XRP price hasn't moved.

2
00:00:03,914 --> 00:00:06,134
But the risk already has.

3
00:00:06,134 --> 00:00:10,904
Most DeFi collateral controls wait for price data to reveal a crisis.

4
00:00:10,904 --> 00:00:14,654
By then, lending markets may already be exposed.

5
00:00:14,654 --> 00:00:18,744
This is RiskOracle, built for interoperable assets on Flare.

6
00:00:18,744 --> 00:00:22,833
Watch the same XRP price as a regulatory shock arrives.

7
00:00:22,833 --> 00:00:25,649
A price-only oracle still reads low.

8
00:00:25,649 --> 00:00:29,557
RiskOracle sends the headline to four independent models.

9
00:00:29,557 --> 00:00:38,064
GPT-5.5 scores 92, Claude Opus 85, DeepSeek 95, and Qwen3 85.

10
00:00:38,064 --> 00:00:42,215
Consensus: 89, before the market reprices.

11
00:00:42,215 --> 00:00:45,200
The models never see one another's answers.

12
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:52,664
RiskOracle exposes their spread and applies divergence-aware consensus, making uncertainty visible instead of hiding it.

13
00:00:52,664 --> 00:00:56,899
The pipeline begins with Flare FTSOv2 market state.

14
00:00:56,899 --> 00:01:02,033
AI adds event, liquidity, volatility, and contagion context.

15
00:01:02,033 --> 00:01:10,734
Because model output is non-deterministic, RiskOracle freezes the result into deterministic JSON for FDC Web2Json attestation.

16
00:01:10,734 --> 00:01:19,314
Here is the proof: deployed Coston2 contracts, immutable RiskUpdated events, and a successful end-to-end FDC transaction.

17
00:01:19,314 --> 00:01:25,673
Continuous demo updates use a lightweight signer; the full FDC path is already proven on-chain.

18
00:01:25,673 --> 00:01:33,562
At risk 95, the FXRP lending example suspends new borrowing, and the insurance pool stops new underwriting.

19
00:01:33,562 --> 00:01:37,251
One signal; policy remains with each protocol.

20
00:01:37,251 --> 00:01:40,516
Built from scratch during Flare Summer Signal.

21
00:01:40,516 --> 00:01:46,571
RiskOracle: verifiable risk intelligence for interoperable assets, before price reacts.
